    "title": "Unrestricted region and scale: Deep self-supervised building mapping framework across different cities from five continents",
    "doi": "10.1016/j.isprsjprs.2024.01.021",
    "doi_url": "https://doi.org/10.1016/j.isprsjprs.2024.01.021",
